citeinfo.othercit: Susan Minnemeyer, Lauriane Boisrobert, Fred Stolle, Y. I. Ketut Deddy Muliastra, Matthew Hansen, Belinda Arunarwati, Gitri Prawijiwuri, Judin Purwanto, and Rakhmat Awaliyan. 2009. Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (CD-ROM). World Resources Institute: Washington, DC.

descript.abstract: This dataset displays detailed roads for Indonesia. It comes from the basemaps of Indonesia, developed by Bakosurtanal. The time period corresponds to the 2003 situation of roads including logging roads. This dataset was prepared by the World Resources Institute for use in the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009).
